Package: PvlTimeSeriesSegmentation
Type: Package
Title: Time Series Segmentation for Viral Load Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: GWMcElfresh
Maintainer: GWMcElfresh <author@example.com>
Description: Provides functions for segmenting viral load time series data by 
    identifying basins and bridges in 2D (value, slope) feature space using 
    kernel density estimation. Classifies temporal regions as basins (high-density) 
    or bridges (low-density transitions between basins).
